  "detailed_description": "<h1>ALSO RECOMMENDED FOR YOU:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Puzzle Light is a Logic Game.<br>The goal in each level is to swap the pieces to form the circuit and turn on the lights.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/ca9e38471b244308197c77af4b9cee46.poster.avif?t=1688079010\" width=478 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/ca9e38471b244308197c77af4b9cee46.webm?t=1688079010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/ca9e38471b244308197c77af4b9cee46.mp4?t=1688079010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/031cad45c55600160ce912ec8064c707.poster.avif?t=1688079010\" width=478 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/031cad45c55600160ce912ec8064c707.webm?t=1688079010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606300/extras/031cad45c55600160ce912ec8064c707.mp4?t=1688079010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 hand-crafted levels;<br></li><li> A fun puzzle game (even for those who have no knowledge of electronic circuits);<br></li><li> At some levels, it is possible to assemble the circuit in more than one way;<br></li><li> If you make a short circuit on battery, it will explode. (Be careful).</li></ul>",
